Name: Average time from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Total time spent in 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' before moving to any other activity
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Average resolution time of cases starting with 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Minimum time from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time it takes 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' after 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Total time it takes cases with 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to reach 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Minimum time it takes from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Accepted + Assigned'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Average time between 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Total resolution time of cases involving 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and ending with 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average time from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Total time for 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Queued + Awaiting Assignment and the end of the case

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' in cases with high impact products
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Completed + Resolved' in cases with medium impact products
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total time from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to 'Accepted + Wait - Customer'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer'
